{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/Layla2.png?t=1739883747\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After having refused to complete a contract, the assassin Layla is banished by her order to a remote island. There to live out her days in exile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/Horns.png?t=1739883747\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But on the island, strange things are happening. Gods and monsters are stirring, and great events are set in motion. Events which will steer Layla unto a new path, and towards a great destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/Horns.png?t=1739883747\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Lantern of Worlds : Layla's Quest</strong> is a short adventure game set in the Lantern of Worlds universe. It is the first game about Layla, her trials and challenges, and her ultimate quest to  exact a great vengeance upon the order that banished her. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/Horns.png?t=1739883747\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as the assassin Layla and explore a mysterious island.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight the good fight, against cultist, drowned pirates, water elementals and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Increase your fighting skills, and learn magic spells of great power!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet with strange allies, pirates and wizards, who will aid you in your</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">quest.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unravel the plans of the fire cult and save the island from their dark rituals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/Horns.png?t=1739883747\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lantern of Worlds - Layla's Quest is also part of the free to play game Lantern of Worlds: Storybook. But this is a much improved version.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/Logo.png?t=1739883747\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3508820?t=1739883747","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3508820?t=1739883747","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/7603e0052f7b6cdcd8bbfa313678798c6a51d404/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739883747","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/7603e0052f7b6cdcd8bbfa313678798c6a51d404/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739883747","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/Layla2.png?t=1739883747\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After having refused to complete a contract, the assassin Layla is banished by her order to a remote island. There to live out her days in exile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.co